    <bioghist encodinganalog="MARC 545"> 
      <head altrender="organization" id="a2">ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY </head> 
      <p>The Africana Studies and Research Center was formally the
        Afro-American Studies Center.</p> 
    </bioghist> 
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520"> 
      <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head> 
      <p>Publicity items, history, lectures, and other ephemera relating to the
        center and Africana studies. Contains course syllabi for courses taught in the
        1970s.</p> 
    </scopecontent> 
